               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431127-name-1332" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1332" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1332" type="surname" value="MOON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1332" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES MOON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Tottenham Court-road. About one o'clock, on the 30th of Nov., I lost some cheroots similar to these—there is my hand<lb></lb>writing on the band which is round them, of the day I had them in.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PRENDERGAST</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> You were not in the shop when they were taken? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431127-name-1333" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1333" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1333" type="surname" value="MOON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1333" type="given" value="SOPHIA"></interp>SOPHIA MOON</persName>
                  </hi>. Between two and three' o'clock, on the 30th of Nov., I was in the parlour—I turned my head, and saw the prisoner take his arm from the window, with a bundle of cheroots in it—I called, "Stop thief"—my husband came out of the back parlour, and pursued him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> You did not see his face? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I saw the side of his face momentarily—there was a glass partition between him and me—he did not appear to be tipsy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431127-name-1334" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1334" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
