                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-1334" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS DOWNHAM</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable E</hi> 47.) I followed the prisoner into a shop in Monmouth-street, and saw another lad with him—the prisoner had this bundle of cheroots in a handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> Where is this street? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> It leads towards St. Giles—he appeared quite sober.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
